European foulbrood of honey bees, Czech Republic
-----------------------------------------
Information received on [and dated] 25 Aug 2015 from Dr Milan Malena, Chief Veterinary Officer, Chief Veterinary Officer, State Veterinary Administration, Prague, Czech Republic

Summary
Report type: immediate notification
Date of start of the event: 13 Jul 2015
Date of confirmation of the event: 13 Aug 2015
Reason for notification: reoccurrence of a listed disease
Date of previous occurrence: reoccurrence of a listed disease
Date of previous occurrence: 1996
Manifestation of disease: clinical disease
Causal agent: _Melissococcus plutonius_
Nature of diagnosis: clinical, laboratory (basic)
This event pertains to a defined zone within the country.

New outbreaks (2)
Outbreak 1: Trutnov, Kralovehradecky
Date of start of the outbreak: 13 Jul 2015
Outbreak status: continuing (or date resolved not provided)
