Epidemiology
Source of the outbreak(s) or origin of infection: unknown or inconclusive
Epidemiological comments: 5-km protection zones around the outbreaks were established.

Control measures
Measures applied: stamping out; no vaccination; no treatment of affected animals
Measures to be applied: movement control inside the country; disinfection/disinfestations; traceability; surveillance outside containment and/or protection zone; official destruction of animal products; zoning

